dct_title_s: Natoliae, quae olim Asia Minor, nova descriptio
dct_description_sm: Relief shown pictorially. This title is part of pl. 52 from the Theatrum oder schawplatz des erdbodems. Antorff : Gielis von Diest, 1572. Text in German on verso: Natolia, oder Klain Asia.
